%N A395341 a(n) = (2*n)! * [x^(2*n)] cosh(x)^3 / cos(x)^2.
%F A395341 a(n) = (3 + 9^n)/4 - (1/2) * Sum_{k=0..n-1} (-4)^(n-k) * binomial(2*n,2*k) * a(k).
%F A395341 a(n) = (1/4) * Sum_{k=0..n} (3 + 9^(n-k)) * binomial(2*n,2*k) * A000182(k+1).
